      "id": "6ba329323035620b",
      "text": "My own experience described here agrees with her claim. I have counted only three occasions when I have experienced being a conspicuous outsider. The entire balance of my life I have been able to pass as an insider. Though I have felt substantial alienation on the inside, I can keep that experience to myself and move around in the world without seeing my own race."
